2019 has seen many successful game launches across various consoles and platforms. These range from sports games to open-world RPGs, and comprise brand-new IPs as well as new iterations from popular franchises. 2020 is expected to be the year that both Sony and Microsoft launch their next-generation PlayStation and Xbox consoles respectively – meaning that it is likely to be a year full of impressive games with improved graphics and features. These are the top 10 video games of 2019 according to Metacritic. Tetris Effect is named after the real phenomenon where players are so engrossed in Tetris that the blocks linger in their mind, vision, and dreams. This is amplified in Tetris Effect, in which the Tetris game includes a 3D world that evolves based on how you play – including the music, backgrounds, sounds, and special effects. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331348" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tetris-Effect-640x430.png" alt="Tetris Effect" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tetris-Effect-640x430.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tetris-Effect-595x400.png 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tetris-Effect-300x202.png 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tetris-Effect-768x517.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Tetris-Effect.png 776w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Monster Hunter: World – Iceborne is a huge expansion for the popular Monster Hunter World. According to Metacritic, the expansion rivals the original in terms of the volume of gameplay. Iceborne transports hunters into an icy region that that includes new monsters and a higher difficulty option while expanding upon the gameplay features that made the original game so popular. <img class="aligncenter 