vaders. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331354" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-640x430.jpg" alt="nier automata" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-640x430.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-596x400.jpg 596w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-768x516.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata-1200x806.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/nier-automata.jpg 1608w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The eleventh instalment in the ever-popular Dragon Quest franchise features brand new characters, as well as an incredible story that will be enjoyable to series fans and new players alike. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331356" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Drago-nQuest-XI-S-Echoes-of-an-Elusive-Age-640x430.jpg" alt="Drago nQuest XI S Echoes of an Elusive Age" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Drago-nQuest-XI-S-Echoes-of-an-Elusive-Age-640x430.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Drago-nQuest-XI-S-Echoes-of-an-Elusive-Age-596x400.jpg 596w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Drago-nQuest-XI-S-Echoes-of-an-Elusive-Age-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Drago-nQuest-XI-S-Echoes-of-an-Elusive-Age-768x516.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Drago-nQuest-XI-S-Echoes-of-an-Elusive-Age.jpg 1072w" sizes="(max-width: 7