o-768x516.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/sekiro-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/sekiro-1200x806.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/sekiro.jpg 1608w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The critically-acclaimed open-world Western made its way to PC in 2019. Red Dead Redemption 2 takes place in 1899 America and sees Arthur Morgan and the Van der Linde attempt to evade federal agents and bounty hunters while simultaneously dealing with internal divisions. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-211900" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Red-Dead-Header.jpg" alt="Red Dead Header" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Red-Dead-Header.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Red-Dead-Header-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Red-Dead-Header-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Resident Evil 2 brings back the various gameplay elements that made the original series such a hit. Join new character, police officer Leon Kennedy, as well as college student Claire Redfield in a fight against a zombie infestation. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331370" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-640x430.jpg" alt="resident evil 2" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-640x430.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-596x400.jpg 596w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-768x516.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2-1200x806.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/resident-evil-2.jpg 1608w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Divinity: Original Sin II is set a thousand years after the original game, and expands upon the gameplay of the previous title. Play as a sourcerer who can summon void creatures. The Divine Order is fighting back against sourcerers, including you, which sees you captured and sent to Fort Joy to be “cured.” However, secrets will be uncovered that undermine the Divine Order’s “holy mission”. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331372" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-640x430.jpg" alt="divinity original sin 2" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-640x430.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-768x516.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-1536x1032.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2-1200x806.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/divinity-original-sin-2.jpg 1607w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Here are the top 10 lists for each popular console and platform: